title: Waves All Plugins Bundle v9r20-R2R
description:
Waves All Plugins Bundle v9r20-R2R

Featuring 64-bit support, faster scanning, faster loading, and faster processing, Waves Version 9 opens up new dimensions of high performance plugin power.

Waves V9r20 installers 

The Dave Clarke EMP Toolbox available as a separate installation option.
Cubase 7.5 32bit: fixed crash with StudioRack and some other plugins upon session close.
Live 9 32bit: fixed graphic corruption in plugins with resizeable GUIs.
GTR Tool Rack: stomp menu no longer opens with an offset in StudioRack.
NLS: fixed graphic corruption issues in mac.
PS22: fixed Pro Tools crash in AudioSuite.
SoundShifter: fixed crash in Pro Tools 11 when trying to adjust the multi-text fields.
Element, GTR & GTR Solo Applications: can now choose the Built in Output device.
